    "ConveyorBuild --> ConveyorBuild (next/nextc: peer reference)",
    "PayloadConveyorBuild --> Building (next: forward building reference)"
  ],

  "key_behavioral_notes": [
    "GenericCrafter progress ticks via getProgressIncrease(craftTime); calls craft() at progress>=1 which consumes inputs and offloads outputItems",
    "Drill selects dominantItem via countOre() (prioritizes non-lowPriority, then most tiles, then ID); DrillBuild.updateTile() offloads items when progress>=getDrillTime(dominantItem)",
    "ConveyorBuild holds up to 3 items in parallel arrays (ids/xs/ys); items advance via ys position each tick; pass() forwards to next.handleItem()",
    "UnitFactory uses multiple configs: Integer (plan index), UnitType (plan lookup), UnitCommand; UnitFactoryBuild creates Unit via plan.unit.create(team), wraps in UnitPayload, fires UnitCreateEvent",
    "PayloadConveyorBuild uses step/curStep() gating to pass Payload forward once per cycle; unitOn() moves physical units using moveForce",
    "UnitFactory.initCapacities() dynamically calculates per-item capacities from all plans (max(stack.amount*2)); consumeBuilder multiplied by state.rules.unitCost(team)",
    "UnitBuild.dumpPayload() triggers server-side RPC Call.unitBlockSpawn which calls build.spawned() to reset state"
  ],

